Somme indications for the execution of the examples in this
chapter.
-----------------------------------------------------------

This chapter deals with the vath thread pools, and in particular
with the task centric NPool utility. All codes are portable

Thos directory contains all the examples discussed in the book, 
plus a few additional examples. The sources describe their object
and meaning.

To compile one specific example: make exec_name

To compile all book examples      :  make allbook
To run all book examples          :  make runbook

To compile all additional examples   :  make allsuppl
To run all additional examples       :  make runsuppl

